      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed cooling system including a high-flow water pump. With its high-revving atmospheric induction and balanced 50/50 weight distribution, this example offers the tactile mechanical feedback and analog engagement sought by serious driving purists.",
      "price": 34500.0,
