    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2016 BMW M2 finished in iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed, presenting a deep, mirror-like finish. While the paint is in excellent shape, there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the black Dakota leather remains supple with only very light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the iDrive system and Harman Kardon premium sound, function perfectly. Mechanically, this M2 is in top form; it has a full service history with recent spark plug replacements, a fresh oil service, and a brake fluid flush performed within the last 500 miles. The Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires provide excellent grip with plenty of life left. This is a smoke-free, accident-free example that offers a balanced blend of daily usability and track-ready performance. Included are two keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts.",
